description:
Lazarus is one of the few people to have the privilege of dying twice! Jesus performed one of his greatest and most controversial miracles towards the end of his ministry - the resurrection of Lazarus from the dead. Having been dead for four days, Jesus showed up in Bethany and called him from the grave, bringing joy to his family and friends. However, it also sought deep hatred from the religious leaders for now Jesus’ divinity could not be denied.
